<a href="mailto:fonzie@ibm.net">Ignia</a> of the Rodsent Nife server on Dec. 13, 1999 at 04:46pm said...<br>
*Continued from last comment* 
5. ENA- Lower Gukk in the Reanimated hand room. This one is the only one you need a group for, unless your brave and kamakazi it. Warning the floor is the same color as the rod in this room 
and it makes it very hard to find with the hand and the dar beating on you.
6. Fana- Oasis is correct but the tower is underwater next to the above ground tower, this one is on the top floor of the tower as well.
7. Geza- HH pass is correct, its in the water near the waterfall closest 
to the Tiger Inn, there are 2 waterfalls there, rod is in front of the one closest to the inn.
8. Heda- Erudin is Wrong, it is Qeynos Aquceducts, in the shark pit there.

